HEADWORD: Shroffage
<hw>Shroff"age</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>A money dealer's
commission; also, more commonly, the examination of coins, and the
separation of the good from the debased.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>Webster 1913 Suppl.</source>]</p>

